{"body": "First, Rails doesn't follow semver.\n\nSecond, no one is telling that people can upgrade to the next version, we only prefer to stick the rails version in the Gemfile to the people don't update the rails by mistake when run `bundle update`.\n\nAnd finally, we avoid changes in the API in patch version but sometimes people can use bugged behavior as correct and they application can be broken with a patch upgrade. So even with a stable API a patch update can broke the application.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6127015", "created_at": "2012-06-05T14:57:53Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6610#issuecomment-6127015", "updated_at": "2012-06-05T14:57:53Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6610, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380636bd3543c15100c8a4"}, "id": 6127015, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6610"}
